  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb2 \u0baa\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bb4\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Rain is likely in some parts of the country",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Department of Meteorology has said that the Sabaragamuwa province and Nuwara Eliya and Kandy districts will experience several spells of rain.",
        "Occasional gusty winds of 40-50 kmph are expected over the western slopes of Central Highlands and Western, Southern and Sabaragamuwa provinces.",
        "Light rain is likely over coastal areas from Colombo to Mataravia Galle.",
        "Wind will be from West to South-West direction with wind speed of 30-40 kmph. The wind speed may increase to 50-55 kmph over the coasts from Neekombo to Puttalam and Mannar to Kangesanthurai and from Galle to Pottuvil through Matara and Ambantota.",
        "The seas from Nee Colombo to Puttalam and Mannar to Kangesanthurai and the seas from Galle to Pottuvil via Matara and Ambantota are expected to be rough from time to time."
      ],
